_clearProposal(uint96).details: Removes an expired proposal from the system

params._index: Index of the proposal to clear

announceResults(uint96[]).details: Announces the results of multiple proposals

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to announce

answer(uint96[],uint8[]).details: Records TOAD's answers for multiple proposals

params._answers: Array of answers corresponding to each proposal
params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to answer

canVote(uint96[]).details: Checks if TOAD can vote on specified proposals

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to check

returns.results: Array of boolean values indicating if TOAD can vote on each proposal

clearProposalByIndex(uint96).details: Clears a proposal by its index

params._index: The index of the proposal to clear

clearProposalByTallyId(uint96).details: Clears a proposal by its tally ID

params._tallyId: The ID of the proposal to clear

constructor.details: Initializes the contract with the TOAD address

discoverProposals(uint96[],uint96[]).details: Discovers and registers new proposals in the system

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to register
params._votingPeriods: Array of voting period durations for each proposal

getProposal(uint96).details: Retrieves a proposal by its ID

params._tallyId: The ID of the proposal to retrieve

returns._0: The proposal data without the disablers mapping

hasVotingPower(address).details: Checks if a user has voting power either through delegation to TOAD or token balance

returns._0: bool Whether the address has voting power

isMember(address).details: Checks if an address has delegated to TOAD

returns._0: bool Whether the address has delegated to TOAD

setDisablePower(uint96[]).details: Sets the voting power for specified proposals. This will not disable TOAD's voting ability until toggle is called.

params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to set disable power for

toggle(uint96[],address).details: Toggles the disable power for specified proposals

params._member: The address of the member to toggle disable power for
params._tallyIds: Array of proposal IDs to toggle disable power for

_clearProposal(uint96).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

announceResults(uint96[]).notice: Results can only be announced once per proposal

answer(uint96[],uint8[]).notice: Proposals must be within their valid block period

canVote(uint96[]).notice: This is a gas-intensive operation and should be used off-chain

clearProposalByIndex(uint96).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

clearProposalByTallyId(uint96).notice: Proposal must be past its voting period to be cleared

discoverProposals(uint96[],uint96[]).notice: Clears inactive proposals before registering new ones
